+<article class="card"><h2>Publication controls</h2><ul><li>Source identifier and calculation-engine version</li><li>Location and timezone displayed with every result</li><li>Uncertainty and regional variation notice</li><li>Human review for festival assertions</li></ul></article>
+</section>
